Adding more of this to my 2023 vision board ✨🥂

We went to this AAA Four Diamond Award winner steakhouse - the Grove Steakhouse at @viejascasinoandresort .

We got to the casino and had a lot of fun, but what we were no expecting was to experience such an incredible dinner, and had to come here to share about it with you. It’s SO worth it!

A luxurious cuisine experience, excellent service and ambience. 

We had the Prime Ribeye Cap Steak and Filet Mignon - both were amazing, but the ribeye was absolutely delicious (rich in flavor, extremely soft texture!). Cooked to perfection!
For dessert, the “chocolate mousse” cake was fantastic!

If you ever come to San Diego, I totally recommend it to you and yes, let’s see ourselves living the best moments during 2023! ✨

Dear Insta diary…
I finally got to see the most famous sign in the Planet. ;) 

I remember I used to see postcards about it when I was a kid, still in Brazil, in the country side. It was “just a dream”.

I felt in my heart I could get there one day and my mom simply knew I’d get there. She gave me all her savings in order to buy me a “plane ticket” to my dream (the ticket was expensive I tell you… 🤑😂). I’m forever grateful for all the opportunities and manifestations I live ✨
I just hope that she can see it all from “up there”! 

And yes, as a true Brazilian, I had to do a little samba for my Brazilian fam 🇧🇷 😅
-

Finalmente consegui ver a placa mais famosa do Planeta. ;)

Lembro que eu costumava ver cartões postais quando era criança, ainda no Brasil, no interior. Era apenas “um sonho”.

Eu sentia em meu coração que um dia chegaria aqui e minha mãe simplesmente sabia. Ela me deu todas as suas reservas de dimdim pra me comprar um “passagem de avião” para o meu sonho (eeeeta passagem cara 🤑😂). Sou eternamente grata por todas as oportunidades e manifestações que vivo ✨

Eu só espero que ela possa ver tudo de “lá de cima”!

E sim, como um verdadeira Brasileira, eu tive que dançar um sambinha pro meu povo que amo 🇧🇷😅

*** Loves, this is just a reminder to believe in your dreams NO MATTER what age or circumstances, believe in yourself, have faith and keep going!! ✨ Amores, este é apenas um lembrete para acreditar em seus sonhos, NÃO IMPORTA a idade ou circunstâncias, acredite em si mesmo, tenha fé e continue!!
-
obrigada meu Deus, te amo mãe.

Carnaval in Brazil… Thanks to my beautiful sister @dra.laraelaine who made this day possible!! Love you so much..! After 6 years without visiting Brazil, she gifted me one of the most beautiful Carnaval experiences I’ve ever had! (It was actually our mom’s dream to enjoy carnaval like we used to see only on TV!). I’m so sure our mom is watching it all from “up there”! We love you mom..!

Carnaval is ALWAYS fun, but it was our first time to be so close to the avenue where it all happens…! 

We cried, we danced, we laughed together! And I gotta mention my brother in law too who took so many pics for both of us! Haha, tks coo @andrediasbr !!

I’ll soon post more pics as we’re going to enjoy Carnaval with my lil sis today as well!

-
🇧🇷 
Carnaval no Brasil... Graças à minha linda irmã que tornou este dia possível!! Te amo minha Pin! Depois de 6 anos sem visitar o Brasil, ela me presenteou com uma das mais belas experiências de Carnaval que já tive! (Na verdade, era o sonho da nossa mãe ir ver o carnaval como costumávamos ver apenas na TV!). Tenho tanta certeza de que nossa mãe está assistindo tudo de “lá de cima”’ Nós te amamos, mãe..! 

O carnaval é SEMPRE divertido, mas foi a primeira vez que estávamos tão perto da avenida onde tudo acontece...!

Nós choramos, dançamos, rimos juntos! E eu tenho que mencionar meu cunhado também, que tirou tantas fotos para nós dois! Haha, tks coo @andrediasbr !!

Em breve vou postar mais fotos, pois vamos aproveitar o Carnaval com minha irmãzinha hoje também!

Thank God. Obrigada Deus. ✨🙏🏼
